# graphify — generated locally, not versioned. graphify's own README suggests committing
# graphify-out/, but its post-commit hook rebuilds the graph after every commit, and a rebuild
# rewrites graph.json wholesale: ~95k changed lines on top of each feature commit. The graph is
# cheap to regenerate (`/graphify`) and worthless as history, so it stays out of the repo.
graphify-out/
